<title>INDIA: CRICKET-INDIA V SOUTH AFRICA FIRST TEST SCOREBOARD.</title>
<headline>CRICKET-INDIA V SOUTH AFRICA FIRST TEST SCOREBOARD.</headline>
<dateline>AHMEDABAD, India 1996-11-20</dateline>
<text>
<p>Scoreboard on the</p>
<p>opening day of the first test betwen India and South Africa on</p>
<p>Wednesday:</p>
<p>India 1st innings</p>
<p>Sanjay Manjrekar b Adams		    34</p>
<p>Nayan Mongia lbw De Villiers		 9</p>
<p>Rahul Dravid lbw Symcox		     24</p>
<p>Sachin Tendulkar Rhodes b Symcox	  42</p>
<p>Mohammad Azharuddin run out		 35</p>
<p>V.V.S.Laxman lbw Donald		     11</p>
<p>Sunil Joshi c Hudson b Donald	     16</p>
<p>Javagal Srinath c Cullinan b Donald     14</p>
<p>Anil Kumble not out			   13</p>
<p>Venkatesh Prasad not out		     7</p>
<p>Extras (lb-7 nb-3)			    10</p>
<p>Total (for eight wickets)		  215</p>
<p>Fall of wickets : 1-22 2-63 3-98 4-129 5-159 6-165 7-193</p>
<p>8-196</p>
<p>To bat: Narendra Hirwani</p>
<p>Bowling: Donald 23-11-33-3, De Villiers 15-3-53-1, McMillan</p>
<p>11-4-20-0, Cronje 12-3-8-0, Adams 17-2-46-1, Symcox 21-5-48-2</p>
<p>(3nb)</p>
<p>South Africa - Hansie Cronje (captain), Andrew Hudson, Gary</p>
<p>Kirsten, Daryll Cullinan, Jonty Rhodes, Brian McMillan, Dave</p>
<p>Richardson, Pat Symcox, Fanie De Villiers, Allan Donald, Paul</p>
<p>Adams.</p>
